videos.description: UConn's Napheesa Collier pokes the ball loose and takes it the length of the court for the transition layup.
videos.headline: Collier gets it done on both ends for UConn

videos.description: Connecticut's Kia Nurse fires a pass to Katie Lou Samuelson, who sinks the bucket off the glass.
videos.headline: Nurse's slick pass sets up Samuelson's nice finish

videos.description: Connecticut guard Gabby Williams splits two Mustangs defenders and makes the tough layup, plus the foul.
videos.headline: Williams gets the tough layup to fall

videos.description: Katie Lou Samuelson forces the turnover and then finds Nurse for the transition layup and foul.
videos.headline: UConn finds Kia Nurse for the transition layup

videos.description: UConn's star guard Samuelson comes out hot against the Mustangs, scoring 19 in the first half.
videos.headline: Samuelson dominates first half in win over SMU

videos.description: Katie Lou Samuelson scores 22 points in No. 1 Connecticut's 83-41 win over SMU.
videos.headline: UConn rolls SMU for 99th straight win
